$ System.OperatingSystem (class)
@ System.OperatingSystem

`System.OperatingSystem` provides information like OS version, platform ID etc.

An instance of `System.OperatingSystem` can be obtained from the → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Environment#System-Environment-OSVersion[`OSVersion`] property of `→ Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Environment`.

